---
title: Thai Pork Stir-Fry with Mint and Ginger
description: Thai cuisine may be known for its heat, but it also features more mild recipes that focus on herbs and aromatics. Our spin on a traditional meat and herb stir-fry puts mint and ginger front and center—the pair showers the veggies and pork in bright and cheerful flavors that leap off the plate.
